repository.name: ecommerce-application
repository.description: This project is an e-commerce website built with a microservices architecture, Next.js and Nest.js frameworks, and a MongoDB database. Customers can browse products, add items to cart, checkout with Stripe API, and view order history. Admins can manage products, orders, and customer information.
